because he was in school at Cliffrow

00:17:57.378 --> 00:18:01.160
and on the morrow of the nativity
of Saint John the Baptist

00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:04.370
25th of June, next before the said birth,

00:18:04.370 --> 00:18:08.930
he was so badly beaten at
school that he left school

