What would you normally
have if you were saying,

00:18:18.470 --> 00:18:21.423
you think, 21 years ago, what's missing?

00:18:21.423 --> 00:18:22.610
- A year.
- A year,

00:18:22.610 --> 00:18:27.313
there's no calendar
year, no day of the week,

00:18:28.260 --> 00:18:30.260
there are feast days, there's events,

00:18:30.260 --> 00:18:31.740
that's the way you pattern your time,

00:18:31.740 --> 00:18:34.917
you think about where you
were according to what

00:18:34.917 --> 00:18:39.917
the feast day was and according
to what the (stammers)

00:18:41.640 --> 00:18:45.410
whatever, so the next one, the next,

