clock has a display

00:32:23.440 --> 00:32:26.730
at the top showing the number
of equal hours since sunrise

00:32:26.730 --> 00:32:30.721
and marks every half hour
with a wonderful display.

00:32:30.721 --> 00:32:33.530
It measures the passing
of time using a bowl

00:32:33.530 --> 00:32:36.310
which floats on a water tank
hidden inside the elephant's

00:32:36.310 --> 00:32:39.580
belly, the bowl slowly fills with water

00:32:39.580 --> 00:32:42.863
from a hole in its bottom
and sinks every half hour.

00:32:43.720 --> 00:32:46.410
When the bowl sinks, it
tugs a series of pullies

00:32:46.410 --> 00:32:49.153
and mechanisms connected
to the top of the clock.

00:32:51.130 --> 00:32:53.930
At the top of the clock, it
