00:33:08.812 --> 00:33:12.510
It causes a cymbal to sound
and makes the elephant driver

00:33:12.510 --> 00:33:15.023
beat his drum and the
body of the elephant.

00:33:16.310 --> 00:33:18.690
As the ball falls out
of the elephant's mouth,

00:33:18.690 --> 00:33:20.890
the floating bowl is pulled back up

00:33:20.890 --> 00:33:22.740
and starts filling with water again

00:33:22.740 --> 00:33:24.293
for the next half hour.

00:33:26.390 --> 00:33:28.690
