00:42:12.980 --> 00:42:17.030
listening to the cicadas,
listening to the howler monkeys

00:42:17.030 --> 00:42:22.030
and just allowing time to be,
surrounded by this incredible

00:42:24.250 --> 00:42:25.083
jungle.

