00:54:20.420 --> 00:54:23.400
but within the history of the universe,

00:54:23.400 --> 00:54:25.650
what American historian
David Christian calls

00:54:25.650 --> 00:54:29.570
big history, in the 13.8 billion year

00:54:29.570 --> 00:54:31.050
